elements.name: As a user I can create new navigation options

steps.name: I enter "marisela.delvalle93@gmail.com" into input field having className "email"
I enter "12345678" into input field having className "password"
I click on element having className "login"
I click on element that links to "#/settings/design/"
I enter "New navigation" into input field having classNames "gh-blognav-container" "gh-blognav-item" "gh-blognav-label" "gh-input"
I enter "newUrl" into input field having classNames "gh-blognav-container" "gh-blognav-item" "gh-blognav-url" "gh-input"
I click on element having classNames "gh-canvas-header" "gh-btn-blue"
